  "title": "Graduate Associate, Recruitment (Daily Training Provided) #EntryLevel #NJH",
  "description": "<p>Looking to build an exciting career that gives you <strong>opportunities for growth?</strong></p><p>Have the passion in <strong>connecting people</strong> and wants to make an impact to their lives?</p><p>Come and join us today! We are looking for <strong>driven and positive </strong>individuals to work together with us in this <strong>purposeful and challenging</strong> environment.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>What are the Job Responsibilities?</strong></u></p><ul><li>Sourcing for corporate clients and suitable candidates - cold calling included</li><li>Administer the full spectrum of recruitment - from sourcing, screening, recruiting and selection to final offering to successful candidates</li><li>Schedule and conduct interviews for potential candidates</li><li>Oversee the client and candidates' accounts, manage business prospect and development</li><li>Networking and expand channels to drive for corporate sales</li><li>Develop and manage healthy relationships with corporate clients, candidates and team</li></ul><p><u><strong>What are Required?</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum Degree (in any disciple) from recognized institutions</li><li>Positive, enthusiastic and self-driven individuals</li><li>Proficient in interpersonal communication</li><li>Active participation in sports or school activities is an added advantage</li></ul><p><u><strong>Why join us?</strong></u></p><ul><li>No prior experience is required as training is included!</li><li>Mentorship will be provided on the job to guide you along the way</li><li>A meaningful, energetic and vibrant work culture</li><li>Many great opportunities for growth and career progression!</li><li>You are empowered to make decisions and take on leadership roles on the job</li><li>Uncapped incentives with basic salary and benefits</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interest applicants, pls email updated resume to jessie@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Jessie Hoe Huey Miin</p><p>CEI Reg No. R1103861</p><p>EA Lic: 99C4599</p><p><br /></p>",
